meaning_str.bing:
n. 先生（Mr 的全写，书写时不常用）
v. 称…先生
网络. 名仕；薯片先生；叫先生

先生（Mr 的全写，书写时不常用）

先生（Mr的全写）；（Mister）男士（用于姓或职位前）

1.en: Mister Gordon uses words from hip-hop songs to help young people, especially those who grew up with poverty and abuse, as he did.
1.cn: 戈登先生采用希普霍普歌曲中的歌词来帮助年轻人，特别是帮助那些和他曾经一样生活在贫穷和受虐待的环境中的年轻人。

2.en: Oh! -So make it a Bud Light, mister, for giving us all a bigger wiener. -Thank you!
2.cn: 哦！-那么来一杯百威啤酒吧，先生，为给我们更大的香肠。-谢谢！

3.en: My Lord, Mister Zhu-ge has come before you with a plan for fighting Cao Cao. It would not hurt to hear him out.
3.cn: 主公，诸葛先生早已胸怀破曹之策，不妨先听一听他的意见。

1.en: Okay. You, Mister Right Place at the Right Time, call me.
1.cn: 你，天时地利人和先生，跟我联络。

2.en: I'm not alone. I'm with you, Mister... What do they call you?
2.cn: 我不是一个人，我和你在一起，先生……怎么称呼你？

3.en: I'm sorry I brought it up. Yeah. Okay, then, back off, mister!
3.cn: 抱歉我提起这件事。好吧，滚开，先生。

4.en: I know when you're lying. And you were lying about the first one, mister.
4.cn: 我知道你什么时候在撒谎，你第一句说谎了，先生。

5.en: Get back here! I said get back here now! Stop! You take one more move, mister...
5.cn: 快回来! 我说你现在回来! 停下!你再敢往前游一下...

6.en: Whatever it is you want from me, mister, I ain't gonna be worth a damn to you like this.
6.cn: 不管你想从我身上得到什么，先生，我这样对你都毫无价值。

7.en: Sheldon you need to work in the morning. I know! Well then bed mister! Five more minutes!
7.cn: 谢尔顿，你还得早起工作呢。我知道！那还不赶紧睡觉！再给我五分钟嘛！

8.en: Don't well me, mister. We've been worried sick. She could have been dead for all we knew!
8.cn: 少跟我说废话，先生，我们快担心死了，我们都觉得她已经不在人世了。

9.en: Mister I saved your life twice. Okay, I can't tell you how or when or why, but I have done shit that matters.
9.cn: 先生，我曾两次救过您的命，明白吗？我不能告诉你何时怎样，或为何，但我的确做了。

10.en: Hang on a second, mister. What? After you used the facilities at the gas station, did you make a purchase? What?
10.cn: 等等，先生。干嘛？你用过加油站的厕所后买东西了吗？什么？

11.en: Very impressive, Mister... Sullivan. Jimmy Sullivan. Sullivan. Like Bill Sullivan, the Scarer? Yeah. He's my dad.
11.cn: 很有本事，这位…苏利文，詹姆士苏利文。跟惊吓大师比尔苏利文同姓？对，他是我老爸。

12.en: Hey, Ross. What are you doing here? Hey, you know what? You are in our apartment all the time! Okay. This is just a drop in the bucket, mister.
12.cn: 瑞秋，你在这里干嘛？你动不动就往我们的公寓跑，我这只是小小的回应，先生。

13.en: Listen, mister, you're gonna talk to your mother and you're gonna fix this, or that thing I said was gonna do to you the minute you got home, you can do to yourself.
13.cn: 你给我听好了，快去跟你妈妈说，把这件事给老娘处理好，不然之前答应你你一回家就给你的"服务"，你就准备"自己来"吧。
